---
// src/pages/blog.astro
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>dani // blog ✍️</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <main class="blog-container">
    <div class="nav-header">
      <a href="/" class="retro-btn">← back home</a>
    </div>

    <header class="blog-header">
      <h1>✍️ blog posts</h1>
      <p>a collection of stories</p>
    </header>

    <div class="blog-grid">
      <article class="bento-card post-card">
        <div class="post-card-header">
          <span class="post-meta">May 24, 2026 • 🏓 sports & science</span>
          <span class="lang-badge">in Portuguese</span>
        </div>
        <h2><a href="/blog/da-acel-ao-cern">My table tennis trajectory</a></h2>
        <p>I write this thinking about my 14-year-old self, who dreamed of being an Olympian, and needed to know that there were other equally incredible paths out there...</p>
        <a href="/blog/da-acel-ao-cern" class="read-more">read full article →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="bento-card post-card placeholder-card">
        <p class="placeholder-text">[ next article coming soon... ]</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    background-color: #e2e8f0;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .blog-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 750px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .retro-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: black;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0px #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .blog-header h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .blog-header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .blog-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bento-card {
    background: white;
    border: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px #1a1a1a;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .post-card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .post-card h2 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .post-card h2 a {
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .post-card h2 a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .post-meta {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* Slick mini-badge indicating the dual languages */
  .lang-badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    background: #ecfccb;
    border: 1.5px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .post-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .read-more {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .placeholder-card {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    border-style: dashed;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .placeholder-text {
    color: #94a3b8 !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }
</style>
